<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١٣٤ - اسْتِعْمَال حرف الجرّ <span class="c2">«الباء»</span> بدلاً من حرف الجرّ <span class="c2">«من»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">مثال:</span>سَخِرَ به<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">الرأي:</span>مرفوضة<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">السبب:</span>لتعدية الفعل بالباء، وهو متعدٍّ بـ <span class="c2">«من»</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">الصواب والرتبة:</span>-سَخِرَ منه <span class="c4">[فصيحة]</span>-سَخِرَ به <span class="c4">[صحيحة]</span> <a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">التعليق:</span> <span class="c2">(انظر: نيابة حرف الجرّ <span class="c2">«الباء»</span> عن حرف الجرّ <span class="c2">«من»</span>)</span>.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>